name: Royal Treat

reviews.review_text:
Great ambiance and tasty food, serve fresh fish, fish thali was good,
Quick service
Highly recommended

One of the best restaurants in Goa. This is a hidden gem tucked in Madapai, Marcela.
If you love the Goan Fish Thali, this is the place to go!!!
It has shifted from Marcel to a new place in Madapai. This place is away from the hustle bustle of city. Spacious parking available. The restaurant is new with good ambience. Two floors seating. The AC is very good, seats are very comfortable. The menu has a lot of variety with all options available Chinese, American, Mughal, North Indian and authentic Goan dishes available.
The Fish Thali is just superb with choice of Bangdo, Kingfish, Chonak, prawns available.
Everything is fresh and delicious. The service is also very good.
I quenched my thirst also with a refreshing Lime soda. It's a great place to go with family.
I had a very good time here. I would recommend it to all my friends.
Really five star food!!! Keep it up guys.

Really good restaurant. Pictures on their Google Business profile are pretty old, they have renovated the place completely and it looks so much better now. They have AC and comfortable seating. Reasonable pricing and taste was also good!

description:
**Royal Treat: A Hidden Culinary Gem in Marcel**

Nestled in the serene locale of Madapai, Marcel, **Royal Treat** has made quite a splash among food enthusiasts, boasting an impressive rating of **4.3** from **1,250 reviews**. Renowned for its **Goan food**, particularly the **fish thali**, the restaurant has gained recognition as a go-to spot for seafood lovers. Additional highlights from the customer feedback include delightful mentions of **kingfish** and the ambiance of this cozy establishment, pulling it close to the hearts of its satisfied patrons.

### Ambiance & Design
As the reviews suggest, Royal Treat has undergone a significant transformation, rejuvenating its décor to create a charming dining atmosphere. The restaurant features a spacious layout with two floors of comfortable seating, all maintained with efficient air conditioning—perfect for those warmer days in Goa. Visible in the shared photographs, the interior boasts a contemporary design with tasteful furnishings that invite relaxation. The visuals capture bright, engaging spaces accompanied by subtle lighting, creating an inviting backdrop for memorable meals shared with family and friends. A distinct sense of tranquility envelops the venue, away from the hustle and bustle, allowing guests to fully enjoy their dining experience.

### Menu & Culinary Experience
Royal Treat’s menu is a triumph of variety that caters to diverse palates. While the **Goan Fish Thali** takes center stage with its superb offerings—including choices of **Bangdo**, **Kingfish**, **Chonak**, and fresh prawns—there's much more to explore. Diners can indulge in a selection of Chinese, American, Mughal, and North Indian options, ensuring a meal that suits any craving. The presentation is noteworthy, as the vibrant colors and careful plating of each dish elevate the experience. According to a satisfied customer, the freshness and flavor of the fish thali are particularly commendable, suggested as a definite must-try for anyone visiting the restaurant. Those seeking a refreshing drink can enjoy the popular **Lime Soda**, highly praised for its zest and thirst-quenching qualities.

### Customer Experience & Service
The service at Royal Treat earns high marks from patrons, who describe the staff as friendly and attentive, ensuring a seamless dining experience. Feedback highlights the quick service, a crucial aspect of any busy restaurant. Whether it’s a reservation or walk-in visit, the well-organized system appears to accommodate guests efficiently. Many diners express their satisfaction not just with the food but also with the warmth and hospitality of the staff, reinforcing the restaurant's commitment to customer care.

### Popularity & Reviews
The buzz surrounding Royal Treat is palpable, as many customers refer to it as a hidden gem worth discovering. Social media is awash with positive testimonials, further amplifying its reputation. Connoisseurs of Goan cuisine have enthusiastically recommended it to friends and family, praising the exceptional quality of the food. Another review emphasizes the reasonable pricing combined with a rich culinary experience, affirming Royal Treat's exceptional value. 

### Utilizing Visual Content
The shared images contribute significantly to the narrative, showcasing not only the delightful food but also the stunning ambiance of the restaurant. For instance, one image captures the beautifully arranged fish thali, and another highlights the inviting seating areas that encourage longer visits. The photographs paint a vivid picture of the culinary adventure that awaits diners at Royal Treat, further inviting potential customers to partake in the experience.

In summary, **Royal Treat** in Marcel stands out as a delightful dining destination, merging delicious cuisine with an inviting atmosphere, efficient service, and an extensive menu tailored for all. Whether you're stopping by for a quick meal or an extended family gathering, it promises to deliver an exceptional culinary experience that will leave you coming back for more.
